title: Lovely 1 Bed 1 Bath Condo
posting_body: ['3431 Kent St #815 Shoreview, Minnesota 55126', 'Price: $1095.00', 'Deposit: $1095.00', 'Affordable and well cared for 1 bed, 1 bath condo in Shoreview.', 'This complex is tucked away in a residential neighborhood yet close enough to St Paul or Mpls for a great convenience factor.', 'Shared community pool, sauna and fitness center.', '1 assigned underground garage parking w/additional plentiful open lot parking.', 'Unit offers updated maple cabinets in kitchen with tile flooring.', 'Updated Maple bath vanity with tiled shower.', 'Large south facing balcony overlooking the pool and courtyard.', 'Spacious bedroom.', 'Unit comes with storage locker.', 'Coin-Op laundry is down the hall.', 'No pets allowed.', 'Available immediately – 1 yr lease term.', 'Tenant pays electric only!', 'Tenant responsible for $150 move in/out fee to HOA plus $250 refundable HOA damage deposit.', 'Regular damage deposit is equivalent to one month’s rent.', 'Renters insurance required.', 'Section 8 not approved.', 'Info deemed reliable but not guaranteed.', 'Pet Policy: No pets allowed.', 'Property Features', 'Condo', '1 bed', '1 bath', 'Built 1972', '1 Parking Spaces', 'Land is 668 square', 'Floor Area is 668 square', 'Garage', 'Balcony', 'Community pool', 'Fitness Center', 'Ramsey County', 'Sauna', 'Storage Locker', 'Underground Parking Garage', 'Visit our website at <URL> for more information.']
